* Thu Aug 17 2017 15:31:33 +0530 mbhangui@gmail.com 2.2-1.1%{?dist}
Release 2.2 Start 08/05/2017
10/05/2011
1.  use packetsize > 512 to avoid dkim failures for sites having long txt
    records (hotmail.com)
2.  config-fast removed display of DESTDIR
11/05/2017
3.  svscanboot/svscan option run .svscan/run or INITCMD. Use unshare --mount
    option to mount private mounts like custom resolv.conf
4.  svscan - run .svscan/shutdown on SIGTERM
12/05/2017
5.  added inotify program to get file system events
6.  added resolvconf service
15/05/2017
7.  qmailctl bug - use sysconfdir instead of INDIMAILDIR
8.  qmail-remote - use X-SMTPROUTES env variable for setting artificial smtp routes.
    SMTPROUTES takes precendence over X-SMTPROUTES
9.  use environment variable SMTPROUTEFILE, QMTPROUTEFILE, MORESMTPROUTECDB to
    configure smtproutes, qmtproutes, moresmtproutes.cdb filenames
10. smtpd.c - fixed spurious error "no valid cert for gateway
11. qmail-remote.c - fix for SMTPROUTE of the form
    domain:x.x.x.x::penalty:max_tolerance username password
16/05/2017
12. refactored dns_text() function in libdkim, surblfilter.c, dns_text.c,
    dns.c
13. dkimverify.cpp - replace strtok() with strtok_r() for thread safe
    operation.
08/08/2017
14. Port for openssl 1.1.0
23/08/2017
15. smtpd.c - replaced SSLv23_server_method() with TLS_server_method()
16. smtpd.c - fixed ifdefs for openssl 1.0.1 version.
17. qmail-remote.c replaced SSLv23_client_method() with TLS_client_method()
18. use tlsclientmethod, tlsservermethod control files only for openssl
    version < 1.0.1
24/08/2017
19. qmail-smtpd, qmail-remote - improved logging of TLS method errors
26/08/2017
20. smtpd.c qmail-remote.c - fixed readling of tlsservermethod, tlsclientmethod control file
21. smtpd.c - initialize proto.len in smtp_init()
22. qmail-showctl - fixed SIGSEGV
29/08/2017
23. upgraded fetchmail to version 6.4.0
01/09/2017
24. libdkim - dns.cpp. fixed double free of dnresult causing SIGSEGV
25. skip envdir if .svscan/variables directory is missing
26. libdkim - added CXXFLAGS -Wno-delete-non-virtual-dtor -Wno-reorder to configure.ac
27. libdkim - removed compiler warnings
28. qmail-dkim - added missing DKIM_MFREE
09/09/2017
29. indimail-mta, added svctool, systemctl unit file for daemontools package
05/10/2017
30. qmail-cdb.c - fixed wrong control filename display in error message
31. recipients.c use users/recipients instead of control/recipients
11/10/2017
32. renamed systemd unit file indimail.service to svscan.service
12/10/2017
33. upgrade boot scripts if new package has updates
15/10/2017
34. config-fast.sh - fixed syntax error due to unterminated variable
21/10/2017
35. svctool,create_services,postinst - refactored code by improving calls to svctool
22/10/2017
36. fixes for latest clamd/freshclam versions (ClamAV 0.99.2)
37. do systemctl daemon-reload if systemd unit file is changed
38. fixes in upgrade.sh, local_upgrade.sh scripts
39. qmail-greyd.c - fixed search record failure when linked list contained just 1 entry
07/11/2017
40. changed logdir to /var/log/svc
21/11/2017
41. fixed syntax error with --qhpsi option changes in spec/postinst file
42. qmail-greyd.c - added verbose variable to suppress few messages
